summary: A small bat file to cheat the best rings and amulets you can find normaly.
descriptionHtml:
Did you want to have all enchanted jewelry and dont want to type all player.additem command?
Well, i did it for you.

Just type "bat allenchjewelry" in the consol and boom you get the best enchanted jewelry there is. No quest or spezial items.

To "Install" just dropp the text in the Skyrim folder (where the data is located).


I came to this idea because there is a mod called  [size=2]Unlimited Rings And Amulets [/size][size=2][b]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6703/?
It is [/b][/size]not a requierment but it makes more sence to use it with this.

There is a file were you get the jewelry equipted and that requiers the mod
